Package: add-relay
Architecture: amd64
Version: 0.3.18-1
Maintainer: Andreas Mueller <amu@gnoppix.com>
Description: Add Relay Server - Store-and-forward message relay
 Add relay server for offline message delivery. Stores encrypted messages
 until recipients come online.
 .
 Features:
  - WebSocket protocol (ws/wss)
  - SQLite message storage with AES-256-GCM encryption
  - Federation with peer relays
  - CBNP cover traffic (optional)
  - Mix routing delays for metadata protection
Depends: libssl3, libsqlite3-0, libtss2-esys-3.0.2-0, libtss2-tctildr0t64
Section: net
Priority: optional
